    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the pastry is almost cooked, heat a separate, large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a small knob of <strong>butter</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced spring greens</strong>, <strong>remaining chopped garlic </strong>and a small splash of cold water, then cook for 2-3 min or until tender with a bite – these are your <strong>garlicky greens</strong></p>",
